# Styling & Design System

## NativeWind/Tailwind

- Use NativeWind (Tailwind for React Native) via `className` prop
- NO inline `style` prop unless absolutely necessary (e.g., LinearGradient)
- Prefer Tailwind utilities over custom CSS

## Color Palette (Strictly Enforced)

**Source of Truth**: `tailwind.config.js` (`theme.colors`)

Only colors defined in config are available - attempts to use others will fail:
- Background: `bg-bg` (custom `#112`)
- Accents: yellow, cyan, pink, slate (specific shades only)
- Always match shadow colors to border colors (darker shade)
- Date-based color semantics: See `features/Chart/ChartDay.tsx`

## Typography

**Source of Truth**: `tailwind.config.js` (`theme.extend.fontFamily`)

- Font family: **Ubuntu Mono** for everything
- Use `font-mono` class
- No other fonts allowed

## Root Layout Gradient

**Source of Truth**: `app/_layout.tsx` (LinearGradient component) - do not change

## Anti-Patterns

- ❌ Don't use inline styles (except LinearGradient)
- ❌ Don't use non-monospace fonts
- ❌ Don't add colors outside the defined palette
- ❌ Don't forget to add shadow when adding borders
